ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
PrecisAppointment of ROBERT W. PAULSON of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Commissioner of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, to hold office during pleasure, effective November 21, 2011; and authorization of the issuance of a Commission under the Great Seal of Canada to ROBERT W. PAULSON.
